About this property

Imperial Resort Hurghada features a restaurant, outdoor swimming pool, a fitness center and bar in Hurghada. Featuring a garden, the hotel is close to several noted attractions, around 1.2 mi from Arena Beach Club, 5.6 mi from Moods Beach and 0.6 mi from Play Kite beach. At the hotel every room is fitted with air conditioning, a wardrobe, a flat-screen TV, a private bathroom, bed linen, towels and a balcony. Imperial Resort Hurghada offers certain units with pool views, and every room is equipped with a kettle. All units will provide guests with a microwave. Guests at the accommodations can enjoy a continental breakfast. Imperial Resort Hurghada offers a terrace. El Karma Aqua Beach Resort is 1.2 mi from the hotel, while Abu Tig Marina is 5.6 mi away. The nearest airport is Hurghada International Airport, 17 mi from Imperial Resort Hurghada.
